data.description: Absolute Alaskan Dream Property. Unsurpassed privacy on 35 acres, surrounded by DNR land and tucked back behind a long gated driveway. This property has both frontage on a very private lake & 1800 ft of frontage on Crooked Creek. Attention to detail is evident throughout this home. Beautiful woodwork & vaulted ceilings in the spacious greatroom greet you when walking through the front door; a stone fireplace with a view of the lake sits in the center. The open concept, sunny kitchen with sliding glass door opens up to a large second level lake view porch, perfect for entertaining. There is a Greenhouse conveniently located off the kitchen porch as well. Basement level 3 car garage with work shop, finished basement with rec room, refrigerator, and it's own half bath. The land speaks for itself. 35 pristine acres, and healthy stands of spruce. To top it off, this property comes completely furnished and ready to enjoy. Appliances include a brand new washer & dryer as well as lots of recent updates to home; including a new roof, siding, 2 new pellet stoves. Hunting, fishing, wildlife viewing possibilities are endless from here. Property is 2.8 miles to the Kasilof River boat launch, and a short drive to some of the best saltwater fishing in the world.
